						<div class="postbody">I read somewhere that MMC5 can use $4020...$5fff too. Is it correct?
<br />
<br />Since APU registers are internal to the CPU, my wild guess was that you don't need to disable ROM for $4000..$401f. This would allow to have 48K, having pretty simple decoder that only disables first 16K of a 64K ROM, for addresses below $4000.</div>

