				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I have strong doubts about the 'we would probably seen it already' argument. The thing is that at the time when wasting 16K of a 64K ROM became acceptable (near the last days of NES, I think), quality standarts for NES games were really high, with much larger ROM sizes and complex mappers being widely used. So such small improvement could be simply unclaimed.</div>

